object.script:
mode = 0 -- 1 left scan -- 2 right scan -- 3,4,5 wait -- 6 left scan receive -- 7 right scan receive -- 8 decision system
tgtaz = 0 tgtazout = 0 tgtel = 0 tgtelout = 0 tgtdist = 0 FOV = 0.01 LR = 0.5 -- multiple of FOV to shift scans by scanaz = 0 Ldet = -1 --<1 = no det Rdet = -1 --<1 = no det delay = 5 sFOVo = 6 --screen FOV offset deta = 0 Ldetel = 0 Rdetel = 0 maxaz = 0.35 --cancels lock enabled = false
-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() faces = input.getNumber(7) -- 1 for up -1 for down deta = -input.getNumber(8) --detect angle detdist = input.getNumber(9) --detect distance det = input.getBool(3) --detection enabled = input.getBool(4) --enabled setting touch = input.getBool(1) w = input.getNumber(1) h = input.getNumber(2) touchx = input.getNumber(3) touchy = input.getNumber(4)
if faces == 1 then touchx = w - touchx end
if touch == true then mode = 0 tgtaz = (touchx-0.5*w)/(sFOVo*w) end
if enabled == false then mode = -1 end
if mode == 0 then FOV = 0.01 mode = 1 end
if mode == 1 then scanaz = tgtaz-(FOV*LR) Ldet = -1 end if mode == 2 then scanaz = tgtaz+(FOV*LR) Rdet = -1 end if mode == 1+delay and det then Ldet = detdist Ldetel = deta end if mode == 2+delay and det then Rdet = detdist Rdetel = deta end
mode = mode + 1
if mode == 3+delay then if Ldet + Rdet > 0 then FOV = FOV/2 --if math.abs(Ldet - tgtdist) < math.abs(Rdet - tgtdist) then if Ldet > 0 then tgtaz = tgtaz - FOV*LR tgtdist = Ldet tgtel = Ldetel else tgtaz = tgtaz + FOV*LR tgtdist = Rdet tgtel = Rdetel end else FOV = FOV*2 end mode = 1 end
--TT Radar Tracking Module (MVC A2) if tgtaz > maxaz or tgtaz < -maxaz then tgtaz = 0 end if FOV > 0.125 then FOV = 0.125 end if FOV < 0.01 then FOV = 0.01 end
output.setNumber(2,-scanaz) --dish point angle output.setNumber(3,FOV) tgtazout = tgtaz*faces tgtelout = tgtel*faces output.setNumber(4, tgtazout) output.setNumber(5, tgtelout) end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0) -- Set draw color to green if false then screen.drawCircle(w / 2, h / 2, w/2) -- Draw a 30px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(w / 2, h / 2, 0.5) -- Draw a 30px radius circle in the center of the screen screen.drawCircle(tgtx*w*0.5 + (w / 2),tgty*h*0.5 + (h / 2), 1) -- Draw a 30px radius circle in the center of the screen --screen.drawTextBox(0,0,w,h,deta) end if enabled then scrx = w*tgtazout*sFOVo scry = -h*tgtelout*sFOVo sunc = w*FOV*sFOVo/2 --uncertainty screen.drawLine(w/2 - scrx,0,w/2 - scrx,h) screen.drawLine(0,h/2 - scry,w,h/2 - scry) screen.drawCircle(w/2 - scrx,h/2 - scry,sunc)
end end

object.script: function onTick() s=screen mc=math.cos ms=math.sin mp=math.pi ma=math.abs mq=math.sqrt iB=input.getBool iN=input.getNumber isPressed=iB(1) inputX=iN(3) inputY=iN(4) zoom=iN(5) gpsX=iN(6) gpsY=iN(7) a=(iN(8)*(-1))+0.25 ra=iN(9)*(-1) rd=iN(10) tn=iN(12) gpsToggle=iB(13) rTarget=iB(14) rToggle=iB(15) keepWaypoint=iB(16) rClean=iB(17) wd=(iN(11)-iN(8))*2*mp end function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight() if isPressed then onTouch(1) elseif touchscreen and gpsToggle then onTouch(0) end if touchscreen and isPressed and laststate~=(inputX+inputY)then mapX, mapY=map.screenToMap(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,inputX,inputY) laststate=(inputX+inputY) waypointX,waypointY=mapX,mapY elseif not touchscreen then mapX=gpsX mapY=gpsY end s.setMapColorOcean(10,10,10) s.setMapColorShallows(15,15,15) s.setMapColorLand(50,50,50) s.setMapColorGrass(70,70,70) s.setMapColorSand(60,60,60) s.setMapColorSnow(60,60,60) s.drawMap(mapX,mapY,zoom) if not touchscreen then if keepWaypoint and laststate~=nil then toLineX,toLineY=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,waypointX,waypointY) s.setColor(250, 234, 0) s.drawText(5,7,'Dist:'..rnd(mq((ma(waypointX-gpsX)^2)+(ma(waypointY-gpsY)^2)),0)..'m') end drawPosition(w/2,h/2,a) x=w/2 y=h/2 elseif touchscreen then toLineX, toLineY=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,gpsX,gpsY) x=toLineX y=toLineY s.setColor(250,234,0) s.drawText(5,7,'Dist:'..rnd(mq((ma(mapX-gpsX)^2)+(ma(mapY-gpsY)^2)),0)..'m') end if touchscreen or keepWaypoint and laststate~=nil then screen.setColor(250,234,0) screen.drawLine(w/2,h/2,toLineX,toLineY) end rcx,rcy=map.screenToMap(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,x,y) s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawText(5,h-5,50-rnd(zoom,1)..'x') s.drawText(5,0,'GPS:'..rnd(gpsX,1)..', '..rnd(gpsY,1)) s.setColor(0,0,0) s.drawCircle(w-9,h-9,9) s.drawCircle(w-9,9,9) s.drawTriangleF(w-9,0,w-15,15,w-3,15) s.setColor(255,0,0) s.drawText(w-11,9,'N') wdx=w-9+9*mc(wd) wdy=h-9+9*ms(wd) s.drawLine(wdx,wdy,w-9,h-9) if rClean then C=nil c=0 end if rToggle then rla=(ra*mp*2)-(a*mp*2) rx1=gpsX+5000*mc(rla) ry1=gpsY+5000*ms(rla) rx11,ry11=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx1,ry1) rx2=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.15) ry2=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.15) rx21,ry21=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx2,ry2) rx3=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.3) ry3=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.3) rx31,ry31=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx3,ry3) rx4=gpsX+5000*mc(rla+0.45) ry4=gpsY+5000*ms(rla+0.45) rx41,ry41=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,rx4,ry4) s.setColor(0,255,0,10) s.drawCircle(x,y,mq((ma(x-rx11)^2)+(ma(y-ry11)^2))) s.setColor(0,255,0,50) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx21,ry21,rx11,ry11) s.setColor(0,255,0,20) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx21,ry21,rx31,ry31) s.setColor(0,255,0,10) s.drawTriangleF(x,y,rx41,ry41,rx31,ry31) s.setColor(0,255,0) s.drawLine(x,y,rx11,ry11) if C==nil then C={} c=0 end c=c+1 if c-tn>=10 then c=0 end if rd==0 then C[c]={q='e',w='e'} else ox1=gpsX+rd*mc(rla) oy1=gpsY+rd*ms(rla) C[c]={q=ox1,w=oy1} end dOb() end drawPosition(x,y,a) end function dOb() for i,oc in pairs(C) do if oc.q~='e' and oc.w~='e' then ocx,ocy=map.mapToScreen(mapX,mapY,zoom,w,h,oc.q,oc.w) g=255-(c-i) s.setColor(255,0,0,g) s.drawCircleF(ocx,ocy,1) end end end function drawPosition(posx,posy,posa) if not iPIR(posx,posy,0,0,w,h) then cx=w-9 cy=27 s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawCircle(cx,cy,9) posx=cx posy=cy end bla=(posa*math.pi*2) x1=posx+(-5)*mc(bla) y1=posy+(-5)*ms(bla) x2=posx+(-5)*mc(bla-10) y2=posy+(-5)*ms(bla-10) x3=posx+(-5)*mc(bla+10) y3=posy+(-5)*ms(bla+10) s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawTriangleF(x1,y1,x2,y2,x3,y3) end function onTouch(toggleId) if toggleId==1 then touchscreen=true elseif toggleId==0 then touchscreen=false end end function rnd(num,nDP) local mult=10^(nDP or 0) return math.floor(num*mult+0.5)/mult end function iPIR(x,y,rectX,rectY,rectW,rectH) return x>rectX and y>rectY and x<rectX+rectW and y<rectY+rectH end

function onTick() up = input.getBool(3) down = input.getBool(1) if zoom==nil then zoom=17 end zoomspeed=zoom/170 if zoom>0 and down then zoom=zoom-zoomspeed elseif zoom<50 and up then zoom=zoom+zoomspeed end output.setNumber(1, zoom) end

-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() uk = input.getNumber(1) ut = input.getNumber(2) uv = input.getNumber(3) ugor = input.getNumber(4) uvispov = input.getNumber(5) uver = input.getNumber(6)
heading=input.getNumber(7) tBearing=input.getNumber(8) tEnabled=input.getBool(7) marginLR= input.getNumber(9) r= input.getNumber(10) g= input.getNumber(11) b= input.getNumber(12) tr= input.getNumber(13) tg= input.getNumber(14) tb= input.getNumber(15) topl = input.getNumber(16) end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() cx=w/2 h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 255, 0)
xi = uk*5*-1
yi = math.sin(math.acos(uk*5))*-1
x = yi
y = xi*-1
xt = w/2 -- ut+h/2
yt = ut*4*h+h/2 --ut*h/8*3+h/2
x1 = x*2+w/2
y1 = (y*2)+yt
x2 = x*26+w/2
y2 = math.ceil(y*26)+yt
x11 = x*(-2)+w/2
y11 = (y*(-2))+yt
x22 = x*(-26)+w/2
y22 = math.ceil(y*(-26))+yt screen.drawLine(x1, y1, x2, y2) screen.drawLine(x11, y11, x22, y22)
xt = w/2 -- ut+h/2
yt = ut*4+h/2 --ut*h/8*3+h/2
gor = math.ceil(ugor) v = math.ceil(uv) ww = w-40 uverS = math.ceil(uver)
screen.drawTextBox(5, 5, 20, 10, gor, 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(ww, 5, 30, 10, v, 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(w-20, h/2, 20, 10, uverS, 1, 1) screen.drawLine(w/2, h/2, w/2, h/2-12) screen.drawLine(w/2+20, h/2, w/2-20, h/2) if uver > 0 then
screen.drawTriangleF(w-15, h/2, w-5, h/2, w-10, h/2-5)
elseif uver < 0 then
screen.drawTriangleF(w-15, h/2+15, w-5, h/2+15, w-10, h/2+20)
else
end screen.drawTextBox(w*3/4-20, h*3/4+10, 40, 10, math.ceil(topl), 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(w*3/4-40, h*3/4+10, 40, 10, ":", 0, 0) if uvispov < 200 then qv = math.floor(uvispov) screen.drawTextBox(w/5+4, h*3/4, 20, 10, qv, 0, 0)
else end offset= heading-math.floor(heading/5)*5 ticks2= math.ceil((cx-marginLR-offset)/5) x= cx-offset-ticks2*5 h5= math.floor(heading-cx+x)%360
screen.setColor(r, g, b, 100) while(x<w-marginLR) do if (h5/15==math.floor(h5/15)) then screen.drawLine(x, 0, x, 2) if x<w/2-12 or x>w/2+12 then if h5==0 then screen.drawText(x-2, 3, "n") elseif h5==45 then screen.drawText(x-4,3,"ne") elseif h5==90 then screen.drawText(x-2, 3, "e") elseif h5==135 then screen.drawText(x-4,3,"se") elseif h5==180 then screen.drawText(x-2, 3, "s") elseif h5==225 then screen.drawText(x-4,3,"sw") elseif h5==270 then screen.drawText(x-2, 3, "w") elseif h5==315 then screen.drawText(x-4,3,"nw") end end else screen.drawLine(x, 0, x, 1) end x=x+5 h5=(h5+5)%360 end screen.setColor(r, g, b) screen.drawLine(cx, 0, cx, 2) number=string.format("%1.0f", heading) screen.drawText((w-number:len()*5)/2+1, 3, number)
if tEnabled then screen.setColor(tr, tg, tb) relBearing= (heading-tBearing)%360 if relBearing>180 then relBearing= relBearing-360 end x= math.max(marginLR, math.min(cx-relBearing, w-marginLR-1)) screen.drawLine(x, 0, x, 2) screen.drawLine(x-1, 0, x+2, 0) end end

M=math S=screen I=input O=output C=S.setColor F=string.format
g0=9.81/60 iN=I.getNumber t=6
function onTick() t=t<6 and t+1 or 0 -- reduced update rate if t==0 then -- old X,Y,Z=x or 0,y or 0,z or 0 Vx,Vy,Vz=vx or 0,vy or 0,vz or 0 V=v or 0 -- new x,y,z=iN(1),iN(2),iN(3) vx,vy,vz=x-X,y-Y,z-Z v=(vx^2+vy^2+vz^2)^0.5 -- ar=M.acos((vx*Vx+vy*Vy+vz*Vz) / (v*V)) G=ar*v *10 end output.setNumber(1,G) end
